{
  "stem": "15577.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I-- witness every-- every-- you know, this-- you call it a gathering.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know how to call it, because it's-- it was called-- there was a special word found by Germans, which is called akcia.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you cannot now say it is an action, because it was-- it was-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there is no-- not a word that you can translate it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was something that they-- they decided that on this day, on these two days, there will be an-- let's call it for the--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--for this purpose akcia or action.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That means that all Jews of the ghetto have to gather on-- in a special place, which was a big place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we lived very close to this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So if I wanted another, so it was-- and their decision was every time-- we knew it at the time-- this akcia has to bring, let's say 5,000 or 10,000 Jews to be sent away.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they gathered the people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The goal was 5,000-- let's say 5,000 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they gathered them, and they took-- the purpose was to take away the elderly and the sick or the very young or somebody who doesn't work, has no-- no identity card that he works.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was the-- the goal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was announced, everybody who doesn't work, everybody who is sick, everybody who is over let's say 50 or 60 or 70 or something.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they didn't pay too-- too much attention to it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The goal was to fulfill the 5,000, let's say, on this day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So in that moment, they had 5,000, it didn't interest them if they really have only the sick and only the elderly, only the young, only the people who didn't work.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
